{"tid":1059322,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基沙文：我同美斯C朗同level","createTime":"2019-03-13T05:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T07:27:32.000Z","uid":13543,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"30112e8269da560b2d117d4437ed2d58d35e74bf","tid":1059322,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=61e46973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】對於在多個個人獎項的選舉中都不能成為三甲，馬德里體育會前鋒基沙文明顯不是味兒，最近再次表現自己有多厲害。<br />\n<br />\n「我跟基斯坦奴朗拿度、美斯、尼馬、基利安麥巴比是不一樣的球員。我身在頂尖水平，而且仍然可以進步。我希望可以變得更全面，雖然不會一季轟入50球，但在進攻上永遠都希望幫助隊友，為球隊貢獻。」基沙文（Antoine Griezmann）說。<br />\n<br />\n基沙文在金球獎、世界足球先生都3強不入，但他認為自己跟同樣拿過5次金球獎的美斯、C朗，是同一個level：「我認為自己已經跟美斯、C朗身處同一個水平了。我知道還有其他後浪直捲，所以我希望進步、勝利，繼續這樣下去，踢出這樣的足球。」<br />\n<br />\n這名法國國腳在今夏世界盃前，拒絕加盟巴塞隆拿，他自言因為太愛馬德里體育會隊友及教練施蒙尼：「我信任他們，我們為彼此貢獻了很多。我留下來，因為他們給我厚厚的愛，若我是為錢，已經去了中國踢波。」"},{"pid":"0ba1bb51d7a09a60f022ab3c1ec9e731ce453b24","tid":1059322,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0748d6a511d73bcea173cfb90eb1e6d470de557","tid":1059322,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9180c93b1aee6b6f3c0d015723107b3d51d0ab41","tid":1059322,"uid":163405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316572f0053830212fc9eb4e17d0da36b596eea9","tid":1059322,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"又輸比阿朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258a